TY  - JOUR
TI  - On the Value of Sample Separation Information
AU  - Kiefer, Nicholas M.
AB  - [The efficiency gain from observing the sample classification in a disequilibrium or switching model is analyzed. The problem is set up as one of comparing the precisions of estimates based on a joint density with those based on a marginal density. Asymptotic results are obtained for a simple model.]
